;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfxP3M9O-909V8qZdjkhr_YokEMkkXyc63-FHjMUHWMV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0C1J5RZD8%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0C1J5RZD8/">55 英寸</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbKAy92IvXMoSN0MOxS1lliPLwiegRI0pGQiKzerRanO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0C1J5228L%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0C1J5228L/?th=1">65 英寸</a>版本的 TCL Q6 分别降至 378 美元和 498 美元的新低。<a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-tvs-for-gaming-180033983.html">对于游戏玩家来说，这是一款值得注意的预算电视</a>，因为它可以以更快的 120Hz 刷新率玩游戏（尽管分辨率为 1080p 或 1440p，而不是 4K）。然而，它缺乏局部调光和 Mini LED。</p><h2>海信U8K </h2><p><core-commerce id="4fd9188fb3374c909d46b0e242db24ac" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果您愿意支付更多费用来升级电视， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEM3M0g4UFZULz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby00a3UtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImZlMzM0ZDNkLTMxY2ItNDc5ZC1iZjlmLTFmY2RlYmY5ZDk0ZSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQLisbkOx1X1OZg2BK32os3NeIGFXg8EaGsGSju6Ee39&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0