能，而且由于它们不使用苹果制造的芯片，因此不具备自动设备切换和音频共享等 AirPods 风格的功能。我们的 <a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">无线耳机购买指南</a>中的许多选择通常表现更好。但如果你喜欢 Studio Buds + 的造型，并且想要一套比 AirPods Pro 更便宜的 Apple ANC 耳塞，那么在这个价格上它们还是物有所值的。</p><h2> 100 美元 Xbox 礼品卡</h2><p><core-commerce id="cc436f7f625b4574821a01f3e5d9510b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>截至撰写本文时，亚马逊正在以 90 美元的价格出售<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDBGNENGSEZDLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby00a3UtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImZlMzM0ZDNkLTMxY2ItNDc5ZC1iZjlmLTFmY2RlYmY5ZDk0ZSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQpjP8DHQVPpELCBido4tAqJBEk9owTQ9yfCRMWqwk1t&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB00F4CFHFC%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00F4CFHFC/?th=1">100 美元的数字 Xbox 礼品卡</a>。这笔交易不需要太多解释：如果您已经计划购买<a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starfield-review-you-will-like-some-of-it-160046067.html"><em>《Starfield》</em></a> 、几个月的 Xbox Game Pass、来自 Microsoft 在线商店的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Microsoft;elmt:;cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=67071605-d4df-494e-8d9c-c9c236b8bb38&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Microsoft&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NzA3MTYwNS1kNGRmLTQ5NGUtOGQ5Yy1jOWMyMzZiOGJiMzgiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubWljcm9zb2Z0LmNvbS9lbi11cy9zdG9yZS9jb2xsZWN0aW9ucy94Ym94YWNjZXNzb3JpZXM_aWNpZD1YYm94QWNjZXNzQ2F0X0hlYWRlcl9TaG9wQWxsIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJmZTMzNGQzZC0zMWNiLTQ3OWQtYmY5Zi0xZm