》DLC 之后， <em>PowerWash Simulator</em>最新的著名联动作品。 《战锤 40K》资料片也即将推出。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>在即将推出的 DLC 中，经典的时间机器并不是唯一可以用虚拟高压水流清洁的东西。它还拥有布朗博士的货车、山谷钟楼、Holomax 剧院和时间列车。还有 10 项成就或奖杯可供获取。 《回到未来》资料片将于今年晚些时候推出。费用为 8 美元。 </p><div id="4945df27c3b944b5b947d8b21ac77ebb"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bPCUaU935Ec?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/powerwash-simulator-will-let-you-clean-the-grime-away-from-back-to-the-futures-delorean-141050171.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/powerwash-simulator-will-let-you-clean-the-grime-away-from-back-to-the-futures-delorean-141050171.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 76e2856d-b4dd-49d4-床5-590b7d167632</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 01 Sep 2023 14:10:50 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693578684</ingested><modified> 2023-09-01T14:31:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/26e87820-48d4-11ee-8afc-b25e184707f8" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/26e87820-48d4-11ee-8afc-b25e184707f8" widt